name:           rewire-frontend
version:        2.7
synopsis:       A Haskell-to-Verilog/VHDL compiler, front end (HSE plus Crust)
description:    The ReWire front end. The haskell-src-exts pipeline (ReWire.HSE.*), the Crust typed functional IR and its transformations (ReWire.Crust.*), and the pass-pipeline orchestration. Produces a ReWire.Hyle device; depends on rewire-core for the Hyle IR, RTL backends, and shared base.
category:       Language
homepage:       https://github.com/rewire-hardware/ReWire#readme
